@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴通过 OIDC 获取的 access_token
@Gateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000

@ForumComment_PostId = 1999694582291365888
@ForumComment_RootId = 1
@ForumComment_ReplyId = 2
@ForumComment_ReplyUserId = 20000
@ForumComment_ReplyUserName = system

### 获取根评论分页（主链路）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetRootComments?postId={{ForumComment_PostId}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&sortBy=default
Accept: application/json

### 获取子评论分页（懒加载）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetChildComments?parentId={{ForumComment_RootId}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 兼容入口：获取整棵评论树（仅用于观察旧调用）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetCommentTree?postId={{ForumComment_PostId}}
Accept: application/json

### 发表根评论
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": {{ForumComment_PostId}},
  "content": "这是一条测试评论",
  "parentId": null,
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "replyToUserName": null
}

### 发表回复评论
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "我来回复你的评论",
  "parentId": {{ForumComment_RootId}},
  "replyToUserId": {{ForumComment_ReplyUserId}},
  "replyToUserName": "{{ForumComment_ReplyUserName}}"
}

### 发表多级嵌套回复
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "这是第三层的回复",
  "parentId": {{ForumComment_ReplyId}},
  "replyToUserId": {{ForumComment_ReplyUserId}},
  "replyToUserName": "{{ForumComment_ReplyUserName}}"
}

### 更新评论
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "commentId": {{ForumComment_RootId}},
  "content": "这是修改后的评论内容"
}

### 超时评论更新（预期失败）
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "commentId": {{ForumComment_PostId}},
  "content": "尝试修改超过 5 分钟的评论"
}

### 空内容评论更新（预期失败）
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "commentId": {{ForumComment_RootId}},
  "content": ""
}

### 获取评论编辑历史
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetEditHistory?commentId={{ForumComment_RootId}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 发表空内容评论（预期 400）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "",
  "parentId": null
}
